                    <row>
                        <cell rend="tdLeft">who?</cell>
                        <cell rend="tdCom">Most commonly dialects show reflexes of CA <hi rend="italic">man</hi>.</cell>
                        <cell rend="tdCentre">Who is this man? – He is my friend</cell>
                        <cell rend="tdRight">
                            <hi rend="red">mīn </hi>hāda z-zalame? hāda rfīʔi. (huwwe rfīʔi)</cell>
                        <cell rend="tdID"/>
                    </row>
                    <row>
                        <cell rend="tdLeft">whose?</cell>
                        <cell rend="tdCom"/>
                        <cell rend="tdCentre">Whose car is this? – This is our car. It’s small but it’s
                            good.</cell>
                        <cell rend="tdRight">hayy sayyāret <hi rend="red">mīn</hi>? hayy sayyārətna.
                            Hiyye ẓġīre bass mnīḥa. (ẓarīfe)</cell>
                        <cell rend="tdID"/>
                    </row>
                    <row>
                        <cell rend="tdLeft">what?</cell>
                        <cell rend="tdCom"/>
                        <cell rend="tdCentre">Fatima, what are you doing now? – I’m watching TV.</cell>
                        <cell rend="tdRight">
                            <hi rend="red">šū </hi>ʕam-tsāwi hallaʔ yā Fāṭme. – ʿam-ətfarraž
                            ʕa-t-tǝlfəzyōn.</cell>
                        <cell rend="tdID"/>
                    </row>
                    <row>
                        <cell rend="tdLeft">why?</cell>
                        <cell rend="tdCom">Often reflexes reflexes of CA <hi rend="italic">li + ’ayy
                            </hi>or <hi rend="italic">li + ’ayy + šay’</hi>
                        </cell>
                        <cell rend="tdCentre">Why didn’t he come? – I don’t know. </cell>
                        <cell rend="tdRight">
                            <hi rend="red">lēš</hi> mā ʔəža? mā baʕref.</cell>
                        <cell rend="tdID"/>
                    </row>
                    <row>
                        <cell rend="tdLeft">where?</cell>
                        <cell rend="tdCom">Often reflexes of CA <hi rend="italic">fī + ’ayna</hi>
                        </cell>
                        <cell rend="tdCentre">Where is my mobile (phone)? – Here it is!</cell>
                        <cell rend="tdRight">
                            <hi rend="red">wēn </hi>əl-mōbāyl tabaʕi? – lēko l-mōbāyl! </cell>
                        <cell rend="tdID"/>
                    </row>
                    <row>
                        <cell rend="tdLeft">where to?</cell>
                        <cell rend="tdCom"/>
                        <cell rend="tdCentre">Where are you (m./f.) going? – I am going home.</cell>
                        <cell rend="tdRight">
                            <hi rend="red">la-wēn</hi> rāyeḥ/rāyḥa? – ʕal-bēt.</cell>
                        <cell rend="tdID"/>
                    </row>
                    <row>
                        <cell rend="tdLeft">where from?</cell>
                        <cell rend="tdCom"/>
                        <cell rend="tdCentre">Where are you (m./f.; sg./pl.) from? – I am/ We are from
                            Aleppo.</cell>
                        <cell rend="tdRight">
                            <hi rend="red">mnēn</hi> ʔənte/ʔǝnti/ʔǝntu? – ʔana/nǝḥna (naḥna) mǝn Ḥalab. </cell>
                        <cell rend="tdID"/>
                    </row>
                    <row>
                        <cell rend="tdLeft">when?</cell>
                        <cell rend="tdCom"/>
                        <cell rend="tdCentre">Fatima, when did you see Muhammad? – I saw him yesterday. </cell>
                        <cell rend="tdRight">yā Fāṭme, <hi rend="red">ʔēmta</hi> šǝfti Mḥammad? – šǝfto
                            mbāreḥ.</cell>
                        <cell rend="tdID"/>
                    </row>
                    <row>
                        <cell rend="tdLeft">how?</cell>
                        <cell rend="tdCom"/>
                        <cell rend="tdCentre">How are you (m./f.)? – I’m fine.</cell>
                        <cell rend="tdRight">
                            <hi rend="red">šlōnak</hi>? – ʔana mnīḥ.<hi rend="red">šlōnek</hi>? – ʔana
                            mnīḥa.</cell>
                        <cell rend="tdID"/>
                    </row>
                    <row>
                        <cell rend="tdLeft">how much?</cell>
                        <cell rend="tdCom"/>
                        <cell rend="tdCentre">How much is half a kilo of lemons? – It’s 10 Lira. </cell>
                        <cell rend="tdRight">
                            <hi rend="red">ʔaddēš</hi> nǝṣṣ kīlo l-lēmūn? – b-ʕǝšrīn lēra.</cell>
                        <cell rend="tdID"/>
                    </row>
                    <row>
                        <cell rend="tdLeft">how many?</cell>
                        <cell rend="tdCom"/>
                        <cell rend="tdCentre">How many children do you (f.) have? – I have two daughters
                            and three sons.</cell>
                        <cell rend="tdRight">
                            <hi rend="red">kam</hi> walad ʕandek? - ʕandi bǝntēn w-tlǝt ǝwlād.</cell>
                        <cell rend="tdID"/>
                    </row>
                    <row>
                        <cell rend="tdLeft">which?</cell>
                        <cell rend="tdCom"/>
                        <cell rend="tdCentre">In which neighbourhood do you live? – We live in Abu
                            Rammana. </cell>
                        <cell rend="tdRight">b-<hi rend="red">ʔani</hi> manṭʔa sāknīn? – nǝḥna sāknīn
                            ǝb-ʔAbu Rǝmmāne.</cell>
                        <cell rend="tdID"/>
                    </row>
